---
title: Autumn-Spiced Pork Chops with Roasted Brussels Sprouts and Honey Butter Sweet Potatoes
description: These pork chops are rubbed with our blend of cinnamon, cumin, and … magic. They’re seared until golden, then topped with a luscious pan sauce. On the side? Roasted Brussels sprouts and speedy baked sweet potatoes slathered in honey butter. Best of fall flavors, delivered!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/2018w52r4-autumn-spiced-pork-chops-50a615ac.jpg
